          <p xml:id="i-N2WRVXc53U1SKvZuE8jnaa">
            1997/98 J0409 Jo408-418
          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-QSBSkvXWaBNhFv6tUE9fjM">
            Motion till riksdagen
          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-WpSLFBY4MsxtTqy4J9b4Yu">
